1
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:33,100
Episode 196
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

2
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,840
The Stone Clan's mysterious disappearance

3
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,840
has thrown the ancient clans into a panic.

4
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:43,380
The Thunder, Flame, and Medicine Clans allied for survival

5
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:46,680
and targeted the Ancient Clan and Hun Zu.

6
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,120
At this moment,

7
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:51,720
Hun Zu's Six-Star Dou Sheng Hun Qian Mo arrived at Soul Hall,

8
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:56,000
to help Hun Mie Sheng destroy the Celestial Alliance.

9
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,760
Hun Zu's declaration of war has arrived.

10
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:01,640
The Celestial Alliance is in grave danger.

11
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:04,160
Three days hence, atop Fallen Mountain,

12
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:08,040
shall be the final battlefield for survival.

13
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,520
Within the Demon Flame Space,

14
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,040
Though Xiao Yan mastered the Pure Lotus Demon Flame

15
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,880
and condensed the Fire Spirit Xiao Yi,

16
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,840
but whether this unprecedented power

17
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:23,000
can truly help the Alliance turn the tide remains to be seen.

18
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:46,880
At this pace, we will reach the Alliance in half a day.

19
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,600
Then let us make haste.

20
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,760
This way, this way.

21
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,800
Coming.

22
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,920
Put this one here.

23
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,840
Hold it steady.

24
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,810
Everyone, move faster.

25
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,800
Do not slack off.

26
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:09,400
Once we deliver these Demon Flame Stones tomorrow,

27
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:11,000
we can be promoted to the Inner Alliance.

28
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:12,370
Yes!

29
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,600
Hey, slow down, slow down.

30
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,440
Give me a hand.

31
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:16,800
Go, go.

32
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,640
Careful!

33
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:19,920
My foot is pinned under here.

34
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,760
Over here.

35
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,960
Where are you rushing those Demon Flame Stones?

36
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:46,680
Soul Hall.

37
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,190
You fools of the Celestial Alliance,

38
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:09,360
mining Demon Flame Stones on Soul Hall territory...

39
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,440
You seek your own demise.

40
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,720
Today,

41
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:18,280
your heads and the stones shall remain here.

42
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,120
In your dreams!

43
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:21,430
We are dead either way.

44
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,640
Fight them to the death!

45
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:23,960
Right!

46
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,960
Fight them to the death!

47
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,240
Attack!

48
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,040
Yes!

49
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:45,030
Quickly!

50
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:45,920
Form a defensive array!

51
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,200
Kill!

52
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:00,940
Retreat!

53
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,520
Kill them all!

54
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,240
Hang up their heads.

55
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,420
Send them to the Celestial Alliance.

56
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,750
Hang the heads.

57
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:34,910
Send them to the Celestial Alliance.

58
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:39,940
Soul Hall has quite the audacity now.

59
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,520
Retreat!

60
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:01,810
Has Soul Hall's reach extended this far?

61
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,320
Who... who are you?

62
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,040
You killed so many people,

63
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,550
and think you can just leave?

64
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,480
The Alliance's people are not easily slain.

65
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,200
(Such terrifying power...)

66
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,520
Are you all right?

67
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,760
Thank you, Senior, for saving us.

68
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:47,000
We are Xuan Squad, Outer Third Division of the Celestial Alliance.

69
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:50,680
We were tasked with mining Demon Flame Stones.

70
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,320
We shall never forget your saving grace.

71
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,070
- Thank you, Senior.
- Thank you, Senior.

72
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:55,920
Thank you.

73
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,200
Outer Alliance...

74
00:07:57,760 --> 00:08:00,000
The Celestial Alliance has grown significantly.

75
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:03,600
Tend to the wounded first.

76
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,200
Please distribute these elixirs among them.

77
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,080
Yes, Senior.

78
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,840
Thank you, Senior.

79
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,080
(Extraordinary strength.)

80
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,440
(And so generous.)

81
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,760
(Who exactly is this Senior?)

82
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,280
Is it not enough?

83
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,560
I have more.

84
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,800
No, no, no.

85
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:38,760
These elixirs are more than enough.

86
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,600
Thank you for bestowing these elixirs.

87
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:44,520
Our brothers are out of danger now.

88
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,280
Soul Hall has a branch nearby.

89
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,000
It is guarded by a One-Star Dou Sheng.

90
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:54,520
They will sense the Guardian's death.

91
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,880
We had best depart at once.

92
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,400
Dou Sheng...

93
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,600
One-Star, you say?

94
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,600
You know the way, do you not?

95
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,840
Lead me there, if you would.

96
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,270
Lead the way...

97
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,120
What does he mean?

98
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:10,760
Where is he?

99
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,520
Where is the Captain?

100
00:09:19,770 --> 00:09:20,610
Captain!

101
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:21,920
Where have you been?

102
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,480
What happened?

103
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:26,200
He... with but a single move,

104
00:09:27,010 --> 00:09:28,150
a mere flick of his finger,

105
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,000
wiped out the entire branch hall.

106
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,960
Who... who in the heavens is this Senior?

107
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,840
Return and find your regional commander.

108
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:40,120
From this day forth,

109
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,960
you shall be Earth-Rank members of the Inner Alliance.

110
00:09:43,070 --> 00:09:43,910
Tell him

111
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,280
that Xiao Yan sent you.

112
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,320
Xiao... Xiao Yan?

113
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,720
Young Alliance Master Xiao!

114
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,680
Xiao Yan...

115
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:54,790
Is it truly him?

116
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:55,680
Young Alliance Master!

117
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,520
You are the Young Alliance Master!

118
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,400
Tell me

119
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:03,790
what occurred in Central Province since the Demon Flame Space closed.

120
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,840
Yes, Senior.

121
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,160
After the Demon Flame Space closed,

122
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,680
the powers of Central Province were reshuffled.

123
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:13,680
The Stone Clan and Spirit Clan vanished suddenly.

124
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:23,040
(The Stone Clan disappeared inexplicably.)

125
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,880
(Who is the hidden hand behind this?)

126
00:10:25,650 --> 00:10:26,690
(And what is their purpose?)

127
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,800
Brother Xiao Yan.

128
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,600
With the Stone Clan and Spirit Clan gone,

129
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,240
and the three clans suddenly forming an alliance,

130
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,800
the Ancient Clan must have felt the impact too.

131
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,120
So I must return and see for myself.

132
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,520
Indeed.

133
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,880
Go see what troubles the Ancient Clan faces.

134
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,200
Take care on the road.

135
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:51,240
If you need anything, send word at once.

136
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,880
Brother Xiao Yan, you must take care as well.

137
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,720
Once my affairs are settled, I shall come find you.

138
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:12,880
(Two years have passed.)

139
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,560
(The Celestial Alliance has risen to prominence.)

140
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:18,080
(I wonder if Master and the others are well.)

141
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,400
In this coming battle at Fallen Peak,

142
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,480
Hun Zu dispatched many warriors to aid Soul Hall.

143
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,640
The one we must be most wary of

144
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,400
is an elder of Hun Zu.

145
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,280
This man is known as

146
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,240
Hun Qian Mo.

147
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,760
A Six-Star Dou Sheng warrior.

148
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:56,320
It is said he once took part in the siege against Xiao Xuan.

149
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,920
Hun Qian Mo.

150
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:04,430
The ancient clans decreed that anyone above Four-Star Dou Sheng

151
00:12:04,430 --> 00:12:05,560
is forbidden from intervening.

152
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:10,060
Will the Ancient Clan and the three-clan alliance just stand idle?

153
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:16,120
The ancient clans now fear for their survival,

154
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,960
dreading a repeat of the clans' disappearance.

155
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,280
In matters of the outside world,

156
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,210
they have no intention of getting involved.

157
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,640
Hun Zu sending out Hun Qian Mo this time

158
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,960
is likely meant to test their limits.

159
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:36,730
Indeed.

160
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,360
If this man truly intends to act,

161
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,450
we may have to ask the Ancestor to step in and hold him off.

162
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:44,640
But Soul Hall still has its Hall Master and Soul Demon Elder.

163
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,200
If even one of them breaks away,

164
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,200
they could temporarily pin down Senior Xiao Chen,

165
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:53,480
splitting the Alliance's strongest forces.

166
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,630
The other

167
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:56,960
could easily lead Soul Hall

168
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,640
in an attack on the Alliance's main base.

169
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:02,280
If Lady Zi Yan could come to our aid,

170
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:04,200
there might yet be a turning point.

171
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:07,360
Zi Yan would be an immense reinforcement,

172
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:10,960
but the Three Islands' forces are not fully uprooted.

173
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:15,400
She must guard East Dragon Island and cannot come to help us.

174
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:18,930
I can handle Soul Demon Elder,

175
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,280
but as for the Soul Hall Master...

176
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,680
Leave the Soul Hall Master to me.

177
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,160
Xiao Yan!

178
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,320
It is Young Alliance Master Xiao Yan!

179
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:45,320
He has returned!

180
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,320
He has finally returned!

181
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,240
You have all worked hard.

182
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,780
- The Young Alliance Master is back!
- Welcome home!

183
00:13:54,780 --> 00:14:01,710
- Welcome home!
- Young Alliance Master!

184
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:44,640
I told you long ago this lad would not die so easily.

185
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:45,920
This time,

186
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:46,980
you ought to believe it, yes?

187
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,730
You truly succeeded.

188
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,560
You refined the Pure Lotus Demon Fire.

189
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:53,880
Mere good fortune.

190
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,960
What was once thought impossible for any man,

191
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,040
you have accomplished.

192
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,680
I never imagined you would truly succeed.

193
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:08,920
Together, we should be able to hold off the Soul Hall Master.

194
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,200
With his current strength,

195
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:14,640
facing the Soul Hall Master alone poses no problem.

196
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:18,080
Then we need not worry about the decisive battle.

197
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:20,440
By the way,

198
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:23,720
Cai Lin has not emerged since entering the Nine Nether Yellow Springs.

199
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:27,520
Qing Lin and I go to check on her from time to time.

200
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:31,310
She must have encountered some fortune in the depths of the Springs.

201
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,480
We can sense her presence,

202
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:35,640
but we cannot enter the depths of the Springs.

203
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:40,000
I never expected Cai Lin's seclusion would last this long.

204
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:43,240
It seems that once matters here at the Alliance are settled,

205
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,710
I must visit the Nine Nether Deep Ground Python Clan.

206
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:52,840
Over the years, against Soul Hall's relentless encroachment,

207
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:56,760
the Celestial Alliance retreated, defended, and fought with all its might.

208
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,800
From the very first battle,

209
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,720
every drop of sweat we have shed,

210
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:04,080
every drop of blood spilled has been for tomorrow,

211
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:07,040
so we might stand proudly atop Fallen Mountain

212
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:08,320
and tell Soul Hall:

213
00:16:08,580 --> 00:16:09,440
If it is war you want,

214
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,510
then war you shall have!

215
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:12,040
War!

216
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:13,090
War!

217
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:17,280
Soul Hall destroyed my home and tormented my father.

218
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,840
This hatred is carved into my very bones.

219
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,520
Not for a single day have I dared forget.

220
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,640
But I know well

221
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,800
that their cruelty against the Xiao family is but a microcosm.

222
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:29,880
What they seek is not the ruin of one house or one clan,

223
00:16:30,570 --> 00:16:33,490
but to bring all of Central Province to its knees.

224
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:37,720
Today I come not as an avenger to call upon you,

225
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:43,800
but as your comrade, to implore you to fight by my side.

226
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:46,390
Drive out Soul Hall!

227
00:16:46,390 --> 00:16:49,940
Defend Central Province! Drive out Soul Hall!

228
00:16:50,070 --> 00:16:53,400
Defend Central Province! Drive out Soul Hall!

229
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:56,920
Defend Central Province! Drive out Soul Hall!

230
00:16:58,780 --> 00:17:03,240
The decisive clash between Soul Hall and the Celestial Alliance,

231
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:05,880
along with Xiao Yan's return,

232
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:09,840
has reached all major powers at once.

233
00:17:10,080 --> 00:17:12,680
It has drawn the gaze of all Central Province.

234
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:17,800
All wonder who shall have the last laugh,

235
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:22,140
becoming the sole overlord of Central Province.

236
00:17:22,164 --> 00:17:39,764
(Watch the Latest Donoghue Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

237
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:44,160
I hear the Fallen Mountains once housed many clans of Magical Beasts.

238
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,960
Today, they have all cleared out completely.

239
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:49,590
With Soul Hall and the Celestial Alliance at war,

240
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,230
even the slightest collateral impact

241
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:53,440
would spell extinction for their clans.

242
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:56,600
Soul Hall is the overlord of Central Province.

243
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:00,480
Look!

244
00:18:00,580 --> 00:18:01,830
The Soul Hall's forces have arrived.

245
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:43,360
Seven Dou Sheng masters deployed at once.

246
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:46,960
Xiao Yan and his allies are in grave trouble.

247
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:58,960
Why has the Celestial Alliance not yet arrived?

248
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,320
Could it be they have grown afraid?

249
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:08,960
Afraid?

250
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:11,680
The Celestial Alliance has never feared anyone.

251
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:56,240
Our Celestial Alliance has deployed ten Dou Sheng.

252
00:20:21,780 --> 00:20:24,580
Wish to uncover the ultimate secret to reaching the realm of Fight God?

253
00:20:24,980 --> 00:20:27,100
Scan to follow the Battle Through the Heavens account.

254
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:29,660
Get the latest animation updates and exclusive insider news.

255
00:20:29,940 --> 00:20:32,140
The legend ahead shall be forged by your passion.

256
